    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
        <h2 class="h1-responsive index-header my-4">See What Others Say About Your Local Farm!</h2>
    </div>
    <div id="indexCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel>">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/Images/oldcar.jpg" alt="First slide">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-sm-block pl-2 pr-2"
                    style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) !important;">
                    <h2>Reliable Farmers</h2>
                    <a asp-page="/SearchResult">Write your first review</a>
                    <p>For the farmers who trust us to improve their customer experience, farming is not just a job,
                        it's an art and a family tradition that's passed down from generation to generation since the
                        beginning of times.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/Images/pig.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-sm-block bg-dark shadow-1-strong pl-2 pr-2"
                    style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) !important;">
                    <h2>No Factory Farming!</h2>
                    <a asp-page="/SearchResult">Write your first review</a>
                    <p>On Rate My Farmer, our farmers believe that Factory Farming is the main cause of animal suffering
                        and abuse. Therefor, being 100% transparent with the consumers on how they raise their livestock
                        is their primary mission.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/Images/sheeps.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-sm-block bg-dark shadow-1-strong pl-2 pr-2"
                    style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) !important;">
                    <h2>Family Activities</h2>
                    <a asp-page="/SearchResult">Write your first review</a>
                    <p>Most of the farmers also offer on site activities for for the whole family! Discover the farms on
                        Rate My Farmer!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#indexCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon text-dark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#indexCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon text-dark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

